==== SOURCE

https://www.forbes.com/sites/johnkoetsier/2018/08/22/uber-might-be-the-first-ai-first-company-which-is-why-they-dont-even-think-about-it-anymore/#293c7b5f5b62

==== AGENT

Uber customer service

==== GOAL

Cluster customers to understand customer needs.

==== DATA

They collect data from its users that use their app. The drivers and the people getting lifts.

==== METHODS

Machine learning driven clustering.

==== RESULTS

All the data collected helps them understand customer needs. Knowing the customer has helped them better serve customers. Uber has seen 10% increase in efficiency in its customer service.

==== COMMENTS

They're collecting a lot of personal data to better their services.